name: Land [Ice Mountain]
description:
1 of the 5 limited Ice Mountain lands.

This NFT entitles[*] its holder 1 x Land [Ice Mountain] property in my Open World game (In development. ETA release : OCT 2022) 

- Holder will earn 0.5 ZX (In game currency) per week from May 2022 for holding this NFT.

- If a holder decides to burn this NFT, the land will be removed from the game. Holder will still own the empty land but will have limited land controls and will earn bare minimum game benefits.

[*] Full terms and conditions will be released in August 2022.

- Nirav
